==Asking the locals==
===Talking to Ali Morrisane before any other progress===
* '''Ali Morrisane:''' I sent you to learn the whereabouts of my nephew, Ali. Is there any word of him in Pollnivneach?
* '''Player:''' Not yet, I'm afraid.
* '''Ali Morrisane:''' That's not really the news I was hoping for.
* '''Ali Morrisane:'''  But since you've been gone trade has gotten even busier. Will you have a look at my wares?
* {{tselect|Select an Option}}
* {{topt|No, I'm really too busy.}}
** {{tact|end}}
* {{topt|Okay.}}
** {{tact|opens=Ali's Discount Wares.}}

===Talking to Ali the Mayor===
* '''Ali the Mayor:''' Welcome, adventurer, to the town of Pollnivneach, the gateway to Menaphos and Al Kharid. My name is Ali and I'm the mayor of this town. I hope you enjoy your stay here.
* '''Player:''' Thank you. That is one of the warmest welcomes I've ever had! People generally treat travelling adventurers with suspicion.
* '''Ali the Mayor:''' All are welcome here. Now more than ever I suppose.
* '''Player:''' What do you mean by that?
* '''Ali the Mayor:''' There's trouble in town, and a lot of villagers have left as a result. Things are looking dire.
* '''Player:''' I'm looking for someone called Ali.
* '''Ali the Mayor:''' Well, take your pick!
* '''Player:''' I mean I'm looking for a specific Ali. He's Ali Morrisane's nephew.
* '''Ali the Mayor:''' Oh, that Ali! Well, er, your best bet is to ask around town. I'm sure someone will know what he's up to.
* {{tact|end}}

===Talking to Ali the Camel Man===
* '''Ali the Camel Man:''' Welcome to my discount camel store. Can I help you with anything?
* {{tselect|Select an Option}}
* {{topt|A discount camel store?}}
** '''Player:''' A discount camel store?
** '''Ali the Camel Man:''' Yes - it's my great idea - selling camels at discounted prices so that the common man can experience the joys of owning a camel of their very own! They're not just a source of kebab meat you know!
** {{tselect|Select an Option}}
** {{topt|So can I buy a camel then? I'm hungry!}}
*** '''Player:''' So can I buy a camel then? I'm hungry!
*** '''Ali the Camel Man:''' I would never sell one to the likes of you! They are beautiful, majestic creatures, not food! Get out of my shop.
*** {{tact|end}}
** {{topt|Yes, camels are beautiful creatures.}}
*** '''Player:''' Yes, camels are beautiful creatures.
*** '''Ali the Camel Man:''' Ah, wondrous camels! Best of all Saradomin's creations. Ships of the desert, far more useful than any horse or donkey. Truly, they are a man's best friend.
*** '''Ali the Camel Man:''' Perhaps you'd like a camel of your own? You're in the right place, if so...
*** '''Ali the Camel Man:''' Is there anything else I can help you with?
*** {{tselect|Select an Option}}
*** {{topt|Well yes, actually I would like to ask about something else.}}
**** {{tact|initial}}
*** {{topt|No, but thanks for your time.}}
**** '''Player:''' No, but thanks for your time.
**** {{tact|end}}
** {{topt|Why would I want a camel? All they do is spit and...}}
