*** '''Ali the Camel Man:''' Is there anything else I can help you with?
*** {{tact|above}}
** {{topt|Actually, I think I was a camel in a previous life.}}
*** '''Player:''' Actually, I think I was a camel in a previous life.
*** '''Ali the Camel Man:''' You're teasing me now! You rogue!
