===Talking to a Street urchin===
* '''Player:''' Hello there!
* '''Street urchin:''' What do you want? Information?
* '''Player:''' What would you know?
* '''Street urchin:''' No one knows what's going on in the streets better than me. I live, sleep, eat and drink here. The fact that I'm so small means that people tend to ignore me which helps even more.
* '''Street urchin:''' Do you need any other information?
* {{tselect|Select an Option}}
* {{topt|Yes tell me about...}}
** '''Player:''' Yes, tell me about...
** {{tselect|Select an Option}}
** {{topt|The Menaphites}}
*** '''Player:''' Tell me about the Menaphites.
*** '''Street urchin:''' They're a bad bunch, always starting fights down in the Asp and Snake. Word on the street is that they're led by some deranged priest. Nobody's ever seen them though - they do all their deals through Ali 'the
*** '''Street urchin:''' Operator'. I reckon they're up to something, but they're such a close knit group that little ever slips out.
*** '''Street urchin:''' Do you need any other information?
*** {{tact|above}}
** {{topt|The bandits}}
*** '''Player:''' Tell me about the bandits.
*** '''Street urchin:''' There's not much to say, really. They're just a group of local thugs led by the biggest and strongest amongst them. If they have any other plans, I don't know about it.
*** '''Street urchin:''' Do you need any other information?
*** {{tact|above}}
** {{topt|The Mayor}}
*** '''Player:''' Tell me about the Mayor.
*** '''Street urchin:''' The mayor is a spineless coward! He never stands up to anybody. That's why the Menaphites are so strong now! He let them stay, and then they started causing trouble. When he realised his mistake, he hired a band
*** '''Street urchin:''' of local thugs to drive them out, but they saw how weak he was and turned on us too. Now we've got bandits and Menaphites, and the mayor isn't doing anything!
*** '''Street urchin:''' Do you need any other information?
*** {{tact|above}}
** {{topt|Ali Morrisane's nephew}}
*** '''Player:''' Tell me about Ali Morrisane's nephew.
*** '''Street urchin:''' I know him! He used to kick us when he caught any of us stealing from his stall.
*** '''Player:''' Do you know where he is now then?
*** '''Street urchin:''' He disappeared a little while ago. All I know is it had something to do with the gangs. Probably he scammed them. You'd have to gain their trust to find out more, m'afraid - if I get too close, they might disappear me
*** '''Street urchin:''' too!
*** '''Street urchin:''' Do you need any other information?
*** {{tact|above}}
** {{topt|The town}}
*** '''Player:''' Tell me about the town.
*** '''Street urchin:''' It's boring! We're not as big as Menaphos or as powerful as Al Kharid, and we've got a really nasty crime problem. It's no wonder so many grown-ups have left.
*** '''Street urchin:''' Do you need any other information?
*** {{tact|above}}
* {{topt|No thanks.}}
** '''Player:''' No thanks.
** '''Street urchin:''' Come back if you need any info about anything in the town.
** '''Player:''' I will do thanks.
** {{tact|end}}

