===Talking to Drunken Ali===
====Initial dialogue====
* '''Drunken Ali:''' Ahh, a kind stranger. Get this old man a drink so that he may wet his throat and tell you of the strange happenings in this town.
* {{tact|end}}

====Using the first beer on him====
* '''Drunken Ali:''' Now where were we? Ah yes, Ali Morrisane's wayward nephew.
* '''Player:''' What?! How did you know that's who I was looking for?
* '''Drunken Ali:''' Er... well, he's a real scamp, that lad! I can't imagine a stranger would be asking after anyone else.
* '''Player:''' Hmm. Well go on then, where is he?
* '''Drunken Ali:''' I'd tell you more, but my throat is drying up. This desert climate is an inhospitable one. Get me another beer so that I can continue my tale.
* {{tact|end}}
<!--Varbit 318 changed: 0 -> 1-->

====After the first beer====
* '''Drunken Ali:''' Get this poor, thirsty old man another drink so that he may wet his lips and continue.
* {{tact|end}}

====Using the second beer on him====
* '''Drunken Ali:''' You are too kind, now what were we talking about?
* '''Player:''' Ali Morrisane's nephew.
* '''Drunken Ali:''' Of course! I've known him since he was a wee lad. A right little mischievous beggar...
* '''Player:''' Yes, I can imagine. Do you have any more recent information about him? Where is he?
* '''Drunken Ali:''' Well now, if you had just asked me that in the first place I would have told you directly!
* '''Player:''' You're right, I'm sorry for beating around the bush. Do you know where Ali's nephew is now, though?
* '''Drunken Ali:''' I'd tell you more, but my throat is drying up. This desert climate is an inhospitable one. Get me another beer so that I can continue my tale.
* {{tact|end}}
<!--Varbit 318 changed: 1 -> 2-->

====After the second beer====
* '''Drunken Ali:''' Alas, my throat has dried up, and I cannot speak... perhaps another drink would help?
* {{tact|end}}

====Using the third beer on him====
* '''Drunken Ali:''' Ahh, that hits the spot.
* '''Drunken Ali:''' Now which of you two adventurers wanted to know where Ali's nephew is?
* '''Player:''' I think you're seeing double.
* '''Drunken Ali:''' Is this a double? No wonder I feel sick...
* '''Player:''' Look, all I want to know is the whereabouts of Ali Morrisane's nephew.
* '''Drunken Ali:''' Now is that his nephew from his side or his wife's? They have a huge family you see. I remember...
* '''Player:''' No, no, no. Stop right there. You are not going to fool me into buying you another beer without first giving me some useful information.
* '''Drunken Ali:''' But my lips are so dry, how can I possibly continue?
* '''Player:''' Well if your lips are dry, I'll have to wring you like a wet cloth and squeeze out enough booze to fill another tankard. I'd reckon it would hurt though.
* '''Drunken Ali:''' I see. Don't worry about me, I'll just have to soldier on. Now what do you want to know?
* '''Player:''' For the last time, where is Ali Morrisane's nephew?
* '''Drunken Ali:''' Oh, I don't know.
* '''Player:''' Seriously?
* '''Drunken Ali:''' Wait, wait! The last I heard he was in trouble with those gangs hanging around town. You won't get any answers out of them, though, not while they're feuding. Maybe if you were to solve that little problem... 
* '''Drunken Ali:''' Anyway, is there any chance of another beer?
* '''Player:''' What do you think?
<!--Varbit 318 changed: 2 -> 3-->
<!--Varbit 334 changed: 1 -> 2-->
* {{tact|end}}

====After the third beer====
* '''Drunken Ali:''' What were we talking about again? Yes yes, when I was a boy... no, that's not it.
* {{tact|end}}

====Using an item other than a beer on him====
* '''Drunken Ali:''' Eh? What's this? I don't want that, get me a beer.
* {{tact|end}}

